snippet.title: Fields of Mistria - Official Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description:
See farming elements and magic, explore the town of Mistria, meet your marriage candidates, and more in this trailer for Fields of Mistria, an upcoming farming/life sim RPG. In Fields of Mistria, start your new life Build the farm of your dreams as you discover a world brimming with possibilities. Magic, romance, and adventure all await you. Fields of Mistria will be available on PC in 2024.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
